ast.bexp

Class CExpBExp

  • java.lang.Object
    • ast.bexp.CExpBExp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASTNode<java.lang.Boolean>, BExp, java.io.Serializable

    public class CExpBExp
extends java.lang.Object
implements BExp
    This class represents a boolean expression based on a comparison expression in the abstract syntax tree (AST). It extends the BExp class and implements the eval method to evaluate the expression.
